headline: Cantor Fitzgerald Reiterates Overweight on Molina Healthcare (MOH) Amid HIX Guidance Concerns
summary: Molina Healthcare, Inc. (NYSE:MOH) is one of the best falling stocks to buy now. On July 24, Cantor Fitzgerald reiterated its “Overweight” rating on Molina with a price target of $312.
